'''fim''' is a [[Sindarin]] word meaning "slim, slender".<ref>{{PE|17}}, p. 82</ref>
'''Examples:'''
*''[[Fimbrethil]]''
==Etymology==
''fim'' derives from the [[Sundocarmë|root]] [[PHIM]], and is related to [[Quenya]] ''[[fimbi-]]''.<ref>{{PE|17}}, p. 23</ref>
